Titolo: 4th & Inches

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: 4th & Inches is an American football sports game by Accolade.  It was released for the Commodore 64 in 1987 and ported to Apple IIGS, MS-DOS, Amiga, and Mac OS by Sculptured Software in 1988. It was designed by Accolade co-founder, Bob Whitehead. An expansion pack, Team Construction Disk, was released in 1988.